9. Why This Works

Every unsafe cell decreases health by exactly 1.

From the same cell, having more remaining health is always better than having less.

Therefore, any state with smaller remaining health is dominated and can be discarded.

Using a max heap ensures we expand the most promising states first, while best[][] prevents unnecessary revisits.



